data.description: This 4 Bedroom, split-entry home features an open layout with a designated dining area, two gathering rooms, and a large, level fenced backyard. A fully equipped Kitchen with stainless appliances is nestled between the dining area and the large living room. You'll love the gas log fireplace, back deck and brand new hot tub that conveys. Prime location in the friendly Brackenridge subdivision, close to all of Fairmont's amenities. Click on the immersive virtual tour to see the layout! Measurements & age of home are approximate.
